---
import Base from '@/layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Code of Ethics, Values and Conduct"
  description="The principles that guide every client relationship, every campaign, and every conversation at Ambitions AI."
>
  <section class="bg-white py-16 dark:bg-gray-950 lg:py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 lg:px-8">

      <h1 class="text-3xl font-normal text-gray-900 dark:text-white sm:text-4xl">
        Code of Ethics, Values and Conduct
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
        Ambitions Web Ltd (trading as Ambitions AI and CXSolved.AI) -- Company No. 15387454
      </p>

      <div class="prose prose-gray mt-10 max-w-none dark:prose-invert">

        <h2>Introduction</h2>
        <p>At Ambitions AI, we believe the way we work matters just as much as the results we deliver. This page sets out the principles that guide every client relationship, every campaign, and every conversation we have.</p>

        <h2>Our Values</h2>

        <h3>1. Honesty, even when it's hard</h3>
        <p>We tell you the truth -- including when the news isn't good. If something isn't working, we say so clearly and focus on what we can do about it. We'd rather have a difficult conversation early than let a problem quietly grow.</p>

        <h3>2. Long-term thinking over short-term wins</h3>
        <p>We're not interested in quick fixes that don't last. Our goal is to build strategies and relationships that create real, sustained growth for your business. Your long-term success drives every decision we make.</p>

        <h3>3. Clear communication at every step</h3>
        <p>You'll always know what we're working on, why we're doing it, and how it's going. No jargon, no vague updates, no unexplained delays. We keep things simple and keep you informed.</p>

        <h3>4. Accountability without excuses</h3>
        <p>When something falls short, we take responsibility for it -- plainly and without deflection. We focus on fixing it, learning from it, and doing better.</p>

        <h3>5. Transparency in how we work</h3>
        <p>From pricing to reporting, we keep things open. You'll always know what you're paying for, what we're doing with it, and what results it's producing.</p>

        <h3>6. Empowering you, not creating dependency</h3>
        <p>Our goal is to grow your knowledge alongside your results. We share what we know, explain what we do, and coach you at every step -- because we believe the most valuable thing we can give a client is the confidence and capability to understand their own marketing. The clients who get the most from working with us are the ones who end up needing us least. That's something we're proud of.</p>

        <h2>Our Commitment to You</h2>
        <p>These aren't aspirations -- they're the standards we hold ourselves to every day. If you ever feel we've fallen short of them, we genuinely want to hear about it.</p>
        <p><a href="/contact/">Contact us</a></p>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
